 patient-centered approach designed to restore independence.\n                    ",[73424,73797],"\n                        ADMIRE represents Ayurgreen Hospital&#39;s 25 years of experience in neuro-rehabilitation, bringing\n                        together Ayurveda, Physiotherapy, Occupational Therapy, Speech Therapy, Robotics, and modern\n                        medicine under one integrated, patient-centered approach designed to restore independence.\n                    ",[73424,73797],"\n                        ADMIRE represents Ayurgreen Hospital&rsquo;s 25 years of experience in neuro-rehabilitation, bringing\n                        together Ayurveda, Physiotherapy, Occupational Therapy, Speech Therapy, Robotics, and modern\n                        medicine under one integrated, patient-centered approach designed to restore independence.\n                    ",[82480,82483],[82480,82483],[82845,82848],[82845,82848],[94802,94821],"Parkinson&apos;s Disease",[94802,94821],"Parkinson&lsquo;s Disease",[94802,94821],"Parkinson&#39;s Disease",[94802,94821],"Parkinson&rsquo;s Disease",[110389,110392],[110389,110392],[110705,110708],[110705,110708],[116710,116713],[116710,116713],[117029,117032],[117029,117032],[138919,138933],"Doctor&apos;s visit",[138919,138933],"Doctor&lsquo;s visit",[138919,138933],"Doctor&#39;s visit",[138919,138933],"Doctor&rsquo;s visit",[143919,143922],[143919,143922],[144238,144241],[144238,144241],[169127,169353],"\n                        India&apos;s pioneer in Integrated Ortho-Neuro Rehabilitation, fusing cutting-edge robotic tech with\n                        traditional Kerala Ayurveda to restore movement and dignity.\n                    ",[169127,169353],"\n                        India&lsquo;s pioneer in Integrated Ortho-Neuro Rehabilitation, fusing cutting-edge robotic tech with\n                        traditional Kerala Ayurveda to restore movement and dignity.\n                    ",[169127,169353],"\n                        In